## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="14625-104">屬性或欄位必須是公用的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14625-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="14625-105">包含屬性的類別必須標記為<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14625-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="14625-106">將不會檢測的任何欄位或類別中未標示有這個或其他 WMI 提供者擴充屬性的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14625-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="14625-107">下列範例示範如何使用 ManagementConfiguration 屬性標記的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14625-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to mark a property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="14625-108">這個屬性會公開至 WMI。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="14625-108">This property is exposed to WMI.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read/write property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get and set this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementConfiguration]  
public double ReadableWritableProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
    set { this.propertyValue = value; }  
}  
```
